Interface RecordDao


  • public interface RecordDao
    Data access object(Dao) for the Record entity.
    Author:
    Jake Batchelor

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      List<Record> getAll()
      Query that retrieves all data from the Record entity.
      List<Record.Display> getSummary()
      Query that INNER JOIN's category.tag, record.amount, and record.info on record.tag_id.
      List<Record.Display> getSums()
      Query that takes category.tag and sum(amount) as amount.record where tag_id = category.id and groups by tag_id.
